s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我真係唔明點解 支持曾俊華 = 放棄爭普選<br />\nD人成日話泛民戇鳩鳩爭取廿年民主毫無吋進<br />\n但射落海都唔益你又對爭取民主有咩吋進 <br />\n投白票射落海，泛民呢招都玩左廿年<br />\n最後都俾人話係鳩做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢講全部, 但肯定有部份係<br />\n<br />\n要記得政改表決前, 支持同反對民意差唔多係四五波<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁高估香港人既意志<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人唔反對泛民參與小圈子, 但用埋輿講機器 轟炸哂全世界就好惡頂<br />\n仲有班痴線黃屍, 唔支持薯片既就係鬼, 仲要叫你收聲<br />\n媽, 好惡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有班人話黃絲高質過藍絲, 會好理性客觀咁睇事, <strong>好理性咁睇魚革義士</strong><br />\n人唔笑, 狗都 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17308763_10155004242698346_2708396011350566896_n.jpg?oh=16e77a26e2405ed942b37ff0557fa10b&amp;oe=59593130\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17308763_10155004242698346_2708396011350566896_n.jpg%3Foh%3D16e77a26e2405ed942b37ff0557fa10b%26oe%3D59593130&h=e62e86e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155004242698346&amp;set=a.398809003345.176520.839853345&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10155004242698346%26set%3Da.398809003345.176520.839853345%26type%3D3%26theater&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2fb8829\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155004242698346&amp;set=a.398809003345.176520.839853345&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"faf0aa41c952c58277a3881106fef878e5464eba","tid":159891,"uid":66656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:57:33.000Z","msg":"倒轉左黎睇<br />\n比錯負評"},{"pid":"d12c58c33bf505f884a97f015c502c64bcf05767","tid":159891,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一輪提名: 150票(明票，單票)<br />\n<br />\n第二輪: 提名票最多兼過半既2-3個侯選人出選(暗票，一人多票)<br />\n<br />\n以300提名黎講<br />\n第一輪實